ouch Arcade<br><br>\u201cCook Serve Delicious 3 is a stressful, yet at times relaxing, cooking game. It is so close to being perfect that I can't wait to see what the next iteration brings.\u201d<br>8/10 \u2013 PC Invasion<br><br>\u201cA relentless and strategic kitchen management game, Cook, Serve, Delicious! 3?! rewards hard effort with moments of transcendental clarity, when plates start flowing and everything is slotting into place. It is meditation. I have never felt a greater sense of peace and purpose than when rolling six burritos in less than five seconds. Prescribe it to people who have lost their way.\u201d<br>Rock Paper Shotgun<br>","screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_1c4edd13e9f7b0a9fc2953b43f280adc2304256e.1920x1080.jpg?t=1730575323","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_1c4edd13e9f7b0a9fc2953b43f280adc2304256e.600x338.jpg?t=1730575323"},{"id":1,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_0b974918ba0068e4c7ce2c08776169aa9fb65109.1920x1080.jpg?t=1730575323","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_0b974918ba0068e4c7ce2c08776169aa9fb65109.600x338.jpg?t=1730575323"},{"id":2,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_069b1b16b14f686ee0a414456bf62b39f09f6f56.1920x1080.jpg?t=1730575323","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_069b1b16b14f686ee0a414456bf62b39f09f6f56.600x338.jpg?t=1730575323"},{"id":3,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_c687445f0cf920375b630716e056d86faa525ac1.1920x1080.jpg?t=1730575323","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1000030/ss_c687445f0cf920375b630716e056d86faa525ac1.600x338.jpg?t=1730575323"},{"id